participants.title: Partner at TEEMA Solutions Group Inc

messages.message:
Hey Brian,
Just checking to see if you are hunting for a new and great company?
Thanks!
I definitely am! Just started hunting again, thank you for the connect! How are things looking on your end? I can send a PDF resume later. :)
Excellent. I love PHP and .Net and have extensive experience with both. Can we set up a call next Monday to go over and tonight I will send you that resume. Does that time frame work for you?
Here is a PDF of my resume if you think you have a need for an enthusiastic software developer ;)  Thank you for the connect earlier!

For a senior software developer in Phoenix it is my understanding they make about $75-120k.  I am willing to move on that depending on the opportunity or if they don't plan on using the full breadth of my expertise.  I have spent 6 years working for startups, so that means working nights and weekends and being "on call" pretty much 100% of the time.  If there is a more comfortable 9-5 position I would be happy with the lower end of that.
Perfect! I'll see what I can make happen for you!
Thank you for your time Curtis!

I would really love to work on advanced AI or a supplier of technology for DARPA.  Any ideas?  
https://www.linkedin.com/company/luka-inc
I have no connections there! Looks very cool tho..
Thank you for your time!  Let me know if something arises :)
